<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="active">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Services</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Four service lines.<br>One contractor.</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks — the building-services packages most clients have to procure separately. We hold all four under one entity, with <strong>one Form of Tender, one PM and one accountability chain.</strong></p></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="svc-detail reveal link in" id="meph"><div class="lead-col"><span class="no">01</span><span class="swatch" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span></div><div><h3 class="nm">MEPH</h3><p class="scope">Heating &amp; cooling, HVAC, heat pumps, ventilation and plant installation. First and second-fix electrical, distribution, EV charging, lighting and power. Public health — hot &amp; cold water services and above-ground drainage. Data, structured cabling and IT infrastructure.</p></div><div><p class="aside-l">Market drivers</p><p class="driver">HVAC retrofits, heat-pump installations, energy-efficiency programmes, EV-charging rollout, and new-build and fit-out M&amp;E packages for Tier-1 supply chains.</p><a class="btn line sm" href="/meph/" style="margin-top: 18px;">Explore MEPH →</a></div></div><div class="svc-detail reveal link in" id="commercial"><div class="lead-col"><span class="no">02</span><span class="swatch" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div><h3 class="nm">Commercial Fit-out</h3><p class="scope">Cat-A and Cat-B fit-out, refurbishment, dry-lining, partitioning, joinery and associated finishes. M&amp;E held in-house rather than sub-let — removing the most common source of programme slip.</p></div><div><p class="aside-l">Market drivers</p><p class="driver">Office refurbishment, landlord re-lets and Cat-A / Cat-B fit-out for Tier-1 main contractors and direct occupiers.</p><a class="btn line sm" href="/commercial/" style="margin-top: 18px;">Explore Commercial →</a></div></div><div class="svc-detail reveal link in" id="fabric"><div class="lead-col"><span class="no">03</span><span class="swatch" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span></div><div><h3 class="nm">Fabric</h3><p class="scope">External envelope: cladding and rainscreen, brick and repointing, render, curtain walling and EWI. Flat and pitched roofing. Façade repair and Building Safety Act remediation.</p></div><div><p class="aside-l">Market drivers</p><p class="driver">Building-envelope upgrade programmes, landlord compliance, façade and cladding remediation on Higher-Risk Buildings, and insurance reinstatement works.</p><a class="btn line sm" href="/fabric/" style="margin-top: 18px;">Explore Fabric →</a></div></div><div class="svc-detail reveal link in" id="groundworks"><div class="lead-col"><span class="no">04</span><span class="swatch" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div><h3 class="nm">Groundworks</h3><p class="scope">Hard and soft landscaping, surfacing, boundaries and external finishes — the external environment around the building, on fit-out, refurbishment and new-build schemes.</p></div><div><p class="aside-l">Market drivers</p><p class="driver">New-build enabling works, drainage compliance, and car-park and external-works packages co-ordinated with the trades above.</p><a class="btn line sm" href="/groundworks/" style="margin-top: 18px;">Explore Groundworks →</a></div></div></section><section class="sec"><div class="intro2 reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 40px;"><div><div class="kicker">Accreditations &amp; insurance</div><h2 class="dhead">Audit-ready<br>by default.</h2></div><p class="body">The accreditation and insurance position required for Tier-1 main-contractor supply chains and direct client work — held independently where appropriate, leveraging the Group's stack where it makes sense.</p></div><table class="acc-table reveal in"><thead><tr><th>Accreditation</th><th>Required for</th><th>Status</th><th>Note</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>ISO 9001 / 14001 / 45001</strong></td><td>Quality, environmental &amp; H&amp;S management</td><td><span class="pill plan">In scope</span></td><td class="note">Implementation programme in motion.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Constructionline</strong><span class="note"> (via Group)</span></td><td>Tier-1 supply-chain pre-qualification</td><td><span class="pill on">Held</span></td><td class="note">Held at Group Gold and leveraged for Building Services.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>CHAS / SafeContractor</strong></td><td>Health-and-safety pre-qualification</td><td><span class="pill in">In progress</span></td><td class="note">Aligned with the Group H&amp;S framework.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>NICEIC / NAPIT</strong></td><td>Electrical contracting</td><td><span class="pill in">In progress</span></td><td class="note">Qualified electricians on the team.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Gas Safe Registration</strong></td><td>Gas installation &amp; servicing</td><td><span class="pill in">In progress</span></td><td class="note">Qualified Gas Safe engineers registered.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>F-Gas certification</strong></td><td>Refrigeration &amp; air conditioning</td><td><span class="pill on">Held</span></td><td class="note">Held by the relevant operatives.</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="reveal in" style="margin-top: 36px;"><h3 class="dhead sm" style="font-size: clamp(24px, 2.6vw, 34px); margin-bottom: 12px;">Insurance</h3><p class="body">Employers' and Public Liability cover at <strong>£10m each</strong> — at the levels required for Tier-1 supply-chain appointments. Professional Indemnity (£1–2m) for design-and-build scope, and Contract Works (All-Risks) cover on every project. Full insurance pack available with our PQQ response on request.</p></div></section></div><section class="band green" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Quote · tender · talk</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Send a tender pack,<br>a scope, or a question.</h2><p class="body" style="margin-top: 18px;">Tier-1 pre-qualification, direct quotation or supplier onboarding. We answer to a named human within 24 hours.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Request a quote →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">General enquiry</a></div></div></div></section></div><footer class="foot" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="foot-inner"><div><div class="fwm">AMPM</div><span class="fmer" aria-hidden="true"><span style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></span><p class="ftag">MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks — one accountable contractor for London and the South East. The building-services arm of AMPM Group.</p></div><div><h5>Site</h5><ul><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li><a href="/services/">Services</a></li><li><a href="/work/">Work</a></li><li><a href="/compliance/">Compliance</a></li><li><a href="/about/">About</a></li><li><a href="/contact/">Contact</a></li></ul></div><div><h5>Direct lines</h5><ul><li><a href="mailto:tenders@ampm.co.uk">tenders@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="mailto:hello@ampm.co.uk">hello@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="mailto:suppliers@ampm.co.uk">suppliers@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="mailto:careers@ampm.co.uk">ca